videos.description: Kansas' Frank Mason III takes it himself to score on a layup.
videos.headline: Frank Mason III scores after going coast-to-coast

videos.description: Kansas' Frank Mason III finds Josh Jackson for an alley-oop dunk.
videos.headline: Mason connects with Jackson for alley-oop slam

videos.description: Oklahoma State's Jawun Evans knocks down a 3-pointer to cut into Kansas' lead.
videos.headline: Evans pulls Oklahoma State closer with 3-pointer

videos.description: Oklahoma State's Phil Forte III hits a 3-pointer from way downtown and Kansas' Frank Mason III answers with a 3-pointer of his own for Kansas.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State and Kansas trade 3-pointers

videos.description: Oklahoma State's Jeffrey Carroll makes a 3-pointer to keep Kansas' lead to single digits.
videos.headline: Carroll keeps it close for Oklahoma State

videos.headline: Jackson hits late 3 for Kansas

videos.description: Breaking down the play of Kansas' Frank Mason III and Oklahoma State's Jawun Evans in Kansas' 90-85 victory against Oklahoma State.
videos.headline: Postgame Breakdown of Kansas' 90-85 win over Oklahoma State
